   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>In the module menu, click <uicontrol>Library</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>LIBRARY MANAGEMENT</uicontrol> page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand <uicontrol>Planning</uicontrol>,and then click <uicontrol>ScoringDepartment</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>SCORING DEPARTMENT</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>New</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The new <uicontrol>SCORING DEPARTMENT</uicontrol> page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the<uicontrol>Name</uicontrol> box, enter the name of the department.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the<uicontrol>Description</uicontrol> box, enter the description for the department.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the <uicontrol>Weightage (%)</uicontrol> field, enter the required weightage percentage.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <ph href="../../../../Warehouse/Task_Warehouse/Save_Options.xml#task-9654/SaveRecord"/>
            </p>
         </li>
